Package com.artisans.code.movimento1euro.network

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlertTask
    Asynchronous task to refresh the alert settings from the API.
    ApiManager
    Util class with methods for interacting with the API
    ApiRequestTask
    Abstract class to build and execute the API requests.
    ConnectionBuilder
    Util class used for building the requests used by ApiRequestTask (except for the GET requests).
    LastCausesTask
    Asynchronous task to get the list of past causes from the server.
    LoginTask
    Asynchronous task to execute the login.
    SeenNotificationTask
    Asynchronous task to notify the server that the user has viewed the notification
    UpdateFirebaseTokenTask
    Asynchronous task to send (and update) the new Firebase token to the server.
    UserInfoUpdateTask
    Asynchronous task to refresh the user's personal information (authentication token, id, name, and expiration date.
    VotingCausesTask
    Asynchronous task to get the list of voting causes from the server.
    VotingTask
    Asynchronous task to send a user's vote to the server.
  • Enum Summary

    ApiRequestTask.Request
    Requests supported
    LoginTask.LoginType
    Types of login supported by the LoginTask class
